This song has to be the best on Coke Studio S09 and probably should have featured in the finale.
Coke Studio Pakistan is undoubtedly the best!!!!  I have become a great fan of Coke Studio S09.
Not a day goes by where I do not listen to at least few of the songs from this season.
They have the best singers, drummer, bass guitarist, acoustic guitarists, electronic guitarists, pianists, tabla player, percussionist, best vocalists, best choir and best music arranger.
And Strings, thank you for putting up this show and arranging everything to perfection!
Such an ridiculous amount of talent to have in one country, so jealous and proud!!!
Massive Respect from India.

snippet.textDisplay:
sohni mahinwaal.......story of the night when sohni went to meet mahinwaal through river...Sohni Mahiwal is a tragic love story which reverts the classical motif of Hero and Leader. The heroine Sohni, unhappily married to a man she despises, swims every night across the river using an earthenware pot to keep afloat in the water, to where her beloved Mehar herds buffaloes. One night her sister-in-law replaces the earthenware pot with a vessel of unbaked clay, which dissolves in water and she dies in the whirling waves of the river. 
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sohni_Mahiwal
